during fiscal 2003, we recorded additions of $306 million in intangible assets,
primarily related to the acquisition of navision a/s and rare, ltd., with $19 million allocated to marketing related assets, $97 million to technology-based assets, $162million to contract based assets, and $28 million to customer-related
