volatility of .39 in 2001, .39 in 2002, and .42 in 2003, and risk-free interest rates of 5.3%, 5.4%, and 3.9% in 2001, 2002, and 2003.   note 17earnings per share   basic earnings per share is computed on the basis of the weighted average number of common shares outstanding. diluted earnings per share is computed on the basis of the weighted average number of common shares outstanding plus
